videoSnippet.title: The agadmator Podcast #1 || Maxime Vachier Lagrave
videoSnippet.description:
Check out my game against Maxime here https://youtu.be/88N3UNeNoWM (will be published after the podcast finishes)

Hello everyone! 
This is my first attempt at a podcast so I hope you will enjoy it as my first guest is none other than Maxime Vachier Lagrave. 
We discuss online chess, FIDE Candidates Tournament 2020, chess in general, Maxime's personal life and finish the episode off with some questions from my subscribers.

Listen to the audio version here https://www.buzzsprout.com/1092209/episodes/3771983
Podcast is also available on Spotify and will soon be on Google Podcasts and Apple Podcasts.

Listen to Juga's song about Maxime here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9rX-ZY7XQuA&feature=youtu.be
